  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Start in the left rail, under I-T and Support.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.184,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "The Support group stacks your ticket tools together.",
      "startS": 3.737,
      "endS": 6.19,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Right below Support Tickets sits Help Desk, Zoho.",
      "startS": 6.622,
      "endS": 10.082,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "One is WashCentral's own queue.",
      "startS": 10.534,
      "endS": 12.536,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "The other is meant to mirror a help desk that lives outside the platform.",
      "startS": 12.821,
      "endS": 16.688,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Open Help Desk, Zoho.",
      "startS": 17.197,
      "endS": 18.261,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "The frame loads fine.",
      "startS": 18.461,
      "endS": 19.131,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "It is the data that is missing.",
      "startS": 19.643,
      "endS": 22.7,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Every count across the top shows a dash,",
      "startS": 22.968,
      "endS": 25.238,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "the status and priority filters have nothing to filter,",
      "startS": 25.456,
      "endS": 30.576,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "and the card in the middle says it plainly: Zoho Desk not connected.",
      "startS": 30.848,
      "endS": 32.776,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "The page even hands you the next move, a button straight to its settings.",
      "startS": 33.189,
      "endS": 36.939,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Head to Settings, Integrations, Zoho Desk.",
      "startS": 37.412,
      "endS": 40.557,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "This is the control room for the connection.",
      "startS": 40.978,
      "endS": 43.119,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Whether Zoho talks to WashCentral is read from this one page,",
      "startS": 43.594,
      "endS": 47.252,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "so it's where support work on this integration starts.",
      "startS": 47.616,
      "endS": 50.201,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Look at the header.",
      "startS": 50.64,
      "endS": 51.462,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "A warning badge reads Not Configured.",
      "startS": 51.933,
      "endS": 54.474,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "That's the whole story in two words.",
      "startS": 54.91,
      "endS": 56.819,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "The chips beside it name how the link would work once someone sets it up:",
      "startS": 57.32,
      "endS": 61.131,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "oh-auth, a live view, a server-side token.",
      "startS": 61.578,
      "endS": 65.119,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Run across the four tiles.",
      "startS": 65.52,
      "endS": 67.321,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Connection, not set.",
      "startS": 68.944,
      "endS": 70.449,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Data center, US.",
      "startS": 70.674,
      "endS": 72.202,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Sync direction, both.",
      "startS": 72.425,
      "endS": 73.902,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "So the tenant has picked how it wants to sync, but no one has authorized the link yet.",
      "startS": 74.793,
      "endS": 79.171,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Drop into the Credentials group.",
      "startS": 79.6,
      "endS": 81.196,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Client I-D, blank.",
      "startS": 82.379,
      "endS": 83.524,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Secret, not set.",
      "startS": 83.864,
      "endS": 84.31,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Access and refresh tokens, not set.",
      "startS": 84.666,
      "endS": 86.006,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "With nothing stored here, there's no live line to Zoho,",
      "startS": 86.465,
      "endS": 89.121,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "which is exactly why the Help Desk view had nothing to show.",
      "startS": 89.709,
      "endS": 96.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Keep reading down.",
      "startS": 96.72,
      "endS": 97.725,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Routing, sync, behavior, mapping.",
      "startS": 98.181,
      "endS": 101.297,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "These rules decide where tickets land and which way they flow once the link goes live.",
      "startS": 101.836,
      "endS": 106.231,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Notice Enabled says Yes while the status still says Not Configured.",
      "startS": 106.749,
      "endS": 111.251,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Switched on in intent, not yet connected.",
      "startS": 111.553,
      "endS": 114.279,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Two tabs sit under the header.",
      "startS": 114.72,
      "endS": 116.395,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Settings, where you are, and Instructions.",
      "startS": 116.86,
      "endS": 119.732,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "The full setup walk-through lives under Instructions, and in lesson twelve point nine.",
      "startS": 120.238,
      "endS": 124.674,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "For today, stay on Settings and just read.",
      "startS": 125.209,
      "endS": 127.806,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Top right, two buttons.",
      "startS": 128.24,
      "endS": 129.709,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Test Connection, and Edit Configuration.",
      "startS": 129.709,
      "endS": 132.569,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Test Connection pings Zoho for real.",
      "startS": 132.569,
      "endS": 135.796,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Edit Configuration opens the credentials.",
      "startS": 135.796,
      "endS": 137.918,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Both touch the live integration,",
      "startS": 137.918,
      "endS": 139.755,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "so neither one gets clicked in a read-only check,",
      "startS": 139.755,
      "endS": 143.061,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "or in support unless the change is yours to make.",
      "startS": 143.061,
      "endS": 146.958,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "So, Help Desk, Zoho.",
      "startS": 147.44,
      "endS": 148.665,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "It's an embedded window into an outside help desk,",
      "startS": 148.868,
      "endS": 149.559,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "empty here because the integration is Not Configured.",
      "startS": 150.127,
      "endS": 152.977,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "When a real client's Zoho tickets go quiet, this is the page you open,",
      "startS": 153.231,
      "endS": 156.293,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "and Token Expiry is the first field you read.",
      "startS": 156.654,
      "endS": 163.651,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "You never have to click Test Connection to know where you stand.",
      "startS": 163.977,
      "endS": 167.247,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}